SCHNEYER--A. Edward, died peacefully in his sleep on January 13th, 2007 at age 95. Devoted husband of 69 years to Kate Schneyer; beloved father of Richard Schneyer, and daughter-in-law Nancy, and the late Susan Preston; proud and loving grandfather of Michael Preston and his wife Karen, Mark Schneyer and his wife Julie, Dr. Lisa Preston, Jeffrey Preston and his wife Lauren Angelillilli, David Schneyer, and Rebecca Schneyer; and adoring greatgrandfather of Ella Schneyer, and Shayna Preston. His family was the light of his life.
